Enable mouse mode                             - :set mouse=n
Disable mouse mode                            - :set mouse-=n
Reformat as csv style 1                       - :Tab /,
Reformat as csv style 2                       - :Tab /,\zs
Save a session                                - :mks
Restore a session                             - :so
set a mark at current cursor location         - m,
jump to next line with a lowercase mark       - ]'
jump to previous line with a lowercase mark   - ['
delete mark a                                 - :delmarks a
delete all lowercase marks for the current buffer (a-z) : :delmarks!

